#. type: Content of: <sect1><title>
#: lfs-en/chapter04/creatingminlayout.xml
msgid "Creating a limited directory layout in LFS filesystem"
msgstr "在 LFS 文件系统中创建有限目录布局"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter04/creatingminlayout.xml
msgid ""
"The first task performed in the LFS partition is to create a limited "
"directory hierarchy so that programs compiled in <xref linkend=\"chapter-"
"temporary-tools\"/> (as well as glibc and libstdc++ in <xref linkend="
"\"chapter-cross-tools\"/>) may be installed in their final location. This is "
"needed so that those temporary programs be overwritten when rebuilding them "
"in <xref linkend=\"chapter-building-system\"/>."
msgstr ""
"在 LFS 分区中需要进行的第一项任务是，创建一个有限的目录树，使得在<xref "
"linkend=\"chapter-temporary-tools\"/>中编译的程序 (以及<xref linkend="
"\"chapter-cross-tools\"/>中的 glibc 和 libstdc++) 可以被安装到它们的最终位"
"置。这样，在<xref linkend=\"chapter-building-system\"/>中重新构建它们时，就能"
"直接覆盖这些临时程序。"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter04/creatingminlayout.xml
msgid ""
"Create the required directory layout by running the following as <systemitem "
"class=\"username\">root</systemitem>:"
msgstr ""
"以 <systemitem class=\"username\">root</systemitem> 身份，执行以下命令创建所"
"需的目录布局："

#. type: Content of: <sect1><screen>
#: lfs-en/chapter04/creatingminlayout.xml
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<userinput>mkdir -pv $LFS/{etc,var} $LFS/usr/{bin,lib,sbin}\n"
"\n"
"for i in bin lib sbin; do\n"
"  ln -sv usr/$i $LFS/$i\n"
"done\n"
"\n"
"case $(uname -m) in\n"
"  x86_64) mkdir -pv $LFS/lib64 ;;\n"
"esac</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>mkdir -pv $LFS/{etc,var} $LFS/usr/{bin,lib,sbin}\n"
"\n"
"for i in bin lib sbin; do\n"
"  ln -sv usr/$i $LFS/$i\n"
"done\n"
"\n"
"case $(uname -m) in\n"
"  x86_64) mkdir -pv $LFS/lib64 ;;\n"
"esac</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter04/creatingminlayout.xml
msgid ""
"Programs in <xref linkend=\"chapter-temporary-tools\"/> will be compiled "
"with a cross-compiler (more details in section <xref linkend=\"ch-tools-"
"toolchaintechnotes\"/>). In order to separate this cross-compiler from the "
"other programs, it will be installed in a special directory. Create this "
"directory with:"
msgstr ""
"在<xref linkend=\"chapter-temporary-tools\"/>中，会使用交叉编译器编译程序 (细"
"节参见<xref linkend=\"ch-tools-toolchaintechnotes\"/>一节)。为了将这个交叉编"
"译器和其他程序分离，它会被安装在一个专门的目录。执行以下命令创建该目录："

#. type: Content of: <sect1><screen>
#: lfs-en/chapter04/creatingminlayout.xml
#, no-wrap
msgid "<userinput>mkdir -pv $LFS/tools</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput>mkdir -pv $LFS/tools</userinput>"
